                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapse_14_4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <p>
                                                Means an individual who is ultimately accountable for ensuring the risk is appropriately managed in a Business Unit. There may be multiple personnel/Business Units who have direct responsibility for, or oversight of activities to manage each identified risk, and who collaborate with the accountable risk owner in his/her risk management efforts such as Directors of Credit Department, IBD, HR.. etc.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>


                                <div class="panel panel-default">
