                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapse_15_4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <p>
                                                Means risk posed by an error or omission in a financial statement due to a factor other than a failure of internal control.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
